    The format of each line is either:

    prog:command [arg [...]]

    or

    command [arg [...]]

    The command field is one of the eeddiittlliinnee(3) built-in commands. Refer to
    BUILT-IN COMMANDS for more information.

    The prog field is the program name string that a program defines when it
